---
title: Beetroot & Feta Falafel with Watercress Salad and Tzatziki
description: Falafel are traditionally made with chickpeas but Mimi has developed this pretty-in-pink version with kidney beans and beetroot. They're lovely to look at but even better to eat. Paired with peppery watercress and cooling tzatziki in a tortilla, you've got tonight's dinner all wrapped up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beetroot-feta-falafel-wk-30-5cef150c.jpg
